Background:
Transformers: Cybertron known as Transformers: Galaxy Force in Japan, is the
animated series which ran from 2005-2006.  It is the third co-production between
Hasbro and Takara.

Transformers: Armada, Transformers: Energon and Transformers: Cybertron, form the
continuity family known as the Unicron Trilogy. 


Plot:
The story centers on a giant black hole that threatens to devour Cybertron and
other worlds.  Only the power of the Omega Lock can stop it; Optimus Prime and a
small team of Autobots travel to various worlds in search of the lock and the four
Cyber Planet Keys needed to activate it.  Megatron, even more obsessed with power
and godhood, attempts to seize the lock and the keys to boost his own personal
power.
